hadiths[22]{hadithnumber,text}:
2025,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Ramazan ke aakhiri Ashrey mein aetikaf kartey they.
2026,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni wafat tak barabar Ramazan ke aakhiri ashrey mein aetikaf kartey rahe aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak beeviyon aetikaf karti rahen.
2027,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Ramazan ke doosrey ashrey mein aetikaf kya kartey they. aik saal Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhi dinon mein aetikaf kya aur jab ikkeeswiin taareekh ki raat aai. ye wo raat hai jiski subah Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aetikaf se bahar aa jatey they, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jisne mere sath aetikaf kya ho wo ab aakhiri ashrey mein bhi aetikaf kare. mujhey ye raat ( khuwab mein) dikhai gaee, lekin phir bhulaa di gaee. maine ye bhi dekha ke usi ki subah ko main keechad mein sajda kar raha hun, isliye tum log usey aakhiri Ashrey ki taaq raat mein talash karo, chunanche usi raat barish hui, masjid ki chhat chunkey khajoor ki shaakh se bani thi isliye tapakney lagi aur khud maine apni aankhon se dekha ke ikkeeswiin ki subah ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki peshani Mubarak par keechad lagi hui thi."
2028,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) masjid mein motakif hotey aur sar Mubarak meri taraf jhukaa detey phir main usmein kangha kar deti, halanke main us waqt haiz se hua karti thi."
2029,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) masjid se ( aetikaf ki haalat mein) sar Mubarak meri taraf hujre ke andar kar detey, aur main usmein kangha kar deti, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab motakif hotey to bila zarurat ghar mein tashrif nahi latey they."
2030,main haaiza hoti phir bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mujhey apne badan se laga letey.
2031,aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) motakif hotey aur main haaiza hoti. iske bawajud aap sar Mubarak (masjid se) bahar kar detey aur main usey dhoti thi.
2032,"umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se arz kya, maine jahiliyat mein ye nazar maana thi ke masjide-Haraam mein aik raat ka aetikaf karunga . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke apni nazar poori kar."
2033,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Ramazan ke aakhiri Ashrey mein aetikaf kya kartey they. main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye (masjid mein) aik khema laga deti aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) subah ki Namaz padh ke usmein chaley jatey they. phir Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ne bhi Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se khema khada karne ki (apne aetikaf ke liye) ijazat chaahi. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne ijazat de di aur unhon-ne aik khema khada kar liya jab Zenab binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anha) ne dekha to unhon-ne bhi (apne liye) aik khema khada kar liya. subah hui to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kai khemey dekhey to farmaya, ye kya hai? aapko unki haqiqat ki khabar di gaee. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, kya tum samajhtey ho ye khemey sawab ki niyat se khadey kiye gaey hain. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us mahina ( Ramazan (ka aetikaf chhod diya aur Shawaal ke Ashrey ka aetikaf kya."
2034,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aetikaf ka irada kya. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us jagah tashrif laey (yani masjid mein) jahan Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aetikaf ka irada kya tha. to wahan kai khemey maujood they. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ka bhi, Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ka bhi aur Zenab (Raziallahu anha) ka bhi, is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kya tum ye samajhtey ho ke unhon-ne sawab ki niyat se aisa kya hai, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wapas tashrif le gaey aur aetikaf nahi kya balke Shawaal ke Ashrey mein aetikaf kya."
2035,"wo Ramazan ke aakhiri Ashrey mein jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aetikaf mein baithey huey they, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se milney masjid mein aaiin thodi der tak baatein kiin phir wapas honey ke liye khadi huin. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi unhein pahunchaney ke liye khadey huey. jab wo Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ke darwazey se qareeb waley masjid ke darwazey par pahunchiin, to 2 Ansari aadmi udhar se guzrey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko salam kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kisi soch ki zarurat nahi, ye to ( meri biwi ( Safiya binte- huyi (Raziallahu anhu) hain. un donon sahaabiyon ne arz kya, Subhan-Allah ! ya Rasulullah ! un par aap ka jumla bada sakht guzra . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke shaitan khoon ki tarah insan ke badan mein daudta rehta hai. mujhey khatrah hua ke kahin tumharey dilon mein wo koi bad-gumaanii na daal de."
2036,"kya aap ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se shabe-qadr ka zikr suna hai? unhon-ne kaha ke haan! ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Ramazan ke doosrey ashrey mein aetikaf kya tha, abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir bees ki subah ko ham ne aetikaf khatm kar diya. usi subah ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein Khattab farmaya ke mujhey shabe-qadr dikhai gaee thi, lekin phir bhulaa di gaee, isliye ab usey aakhiri ashrey ki taaq raaton mein talash karo. maine ( khuwab mein) dekha hai ke main keechad , pani mein sajda kar raha hun aur jin logon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath (is saal ( aetikaf kya tha wo phir dobara karein. chunanche wo log masjid mein dobara aa gaey. aasman mein kahin badal ka aik tukda bhi nahi tha ke achcha badal aaya aur barish shuru ho gaee. phir Namaz ki takbeer hui aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne keechad mein sajda kya. maine khud aap ki naak aur peshani par keechad laga hua dekha."
2037,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aap ki beeviyon mein se aik khatun ( Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ( ne jo haiz ki haalat mein thin, aetikaf kya. wo surkhi aur zardi (yani istihaaze ka khoon) dekhti thin. aksar tasht ham unke nichey rakh detey aur wo Namaz padhti rehtin."
2038,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak biwi Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein khabar di (doosri sanad) aur imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha ke ham se Abdullah-bin Muhammad ne bayan kya kaha ke ham se Hisham ne bayan kya, unhein Mamar ne khabar di, unhein Zohri ne, unhein Ali-bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) masjid main ( aetikaf mein) they aap ke paas paak beeviyon baithi thin. jab wo chalney lagein to aap ne Safiya-binte-Huyi (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya ke jaldi na kar, main tumhen chhodney chalta hun. unka hujra daare-Usama (Raziallahu anhu) mein tha, chunanche jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke sath nikley to 2 Ansari sahaabiyon se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki mulaqat hui. un donon hazraat ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha aur jaldi se aagey badh jana chaha. lekin aap ne farmaya thehro! idhar suno! ye Safiya-binte-Huyi hain (jo meri biwi hain) un hazraat ne arz ki, Subhan-Allah ! ya Rasulullah ! aap ne farmaya ke shaitan ( insan ke jism mein) khoon ki tarah daudta hai aur mujhey khatrah ye hua ke kahin tumharey dilon mein bhi koi ( buri ( baat na daal de."
2039,"Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke yahan aaiin . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt aetikaf mein they. phir jab wo wapas honey lagiin to aap bhi unke sath ( thodi door tak unhein chhodney) aaey. (aatey huey) aik Ansari sahabi (Raziallahu anhu) ne aapko dekha. jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki nazar un par padii, to fauran Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein bulaayaa, ke suno! ye (meri beewii) Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) hain. (Sufiyaan ne hi Safiya ke bajaey kabhi-kabhi (ye Safiya hain) ke alfaz kahey. (iski wazaahat isliye zaroori samjhii) ke shaitan insan ke jism mein khoon ki tarah daudta rehta hai. main (Ali-bin-Abdullaah) ne Sufiyan se puchha ke ghaaliban wo raat ko aai hongii? to unhon-ne farmaya ke raat ke siwa aur waqt hi kon sa ho sakta tha."
2040,"ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Ramazan ke doosrey ashrey mein aetikaf ke liye baithey. beeswiin ki subah ko ham ne apna saman (masjid se) utha liya. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey aur farmaya ke jisne (doosrey Ashrey mein) aetikaf kya hai wo dobara aetikaf ki jagah chaley, kyonke maine aaj ki raat (shabe-qadr ko) khuwab mein dekha hai maine ye bhi dekha ke main keechad mein sajda kar raha hun. phir jab apne aetikaf ki jagah (masjid mein) aap dobara aagey to achcha badal mandlaaey, aur barish hui. us zaat ki qism jisne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko haq ke sath bhejaa! aasman par isi din ke aakhiri hisse mein badal hua tha. masjid khajoor ki shakhon se bani hui thi (is liye chhat se pani tapkaa) jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz subah ada ki, to maine dekha ke aap ki naak aur peshani par keechad ka asar tha."
2041,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) har Ramazan mein aetikaf kya kartey. aap subah ki Namaz padhney ke baad us jagah jatey jahan aapko aetikaf ke liye baithna hota. rawi ne kaha ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bhi aap se aetikaf karne ki ijazat chaahi. aap ne unhein ijazat de di, isliye unhon-ne (apne liye bhi masjid mein) aik khema laga liya. Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) (paak bevi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) ne suna to unhon-ne bhi aik khema laga liya. Zenab (Raziallahu anha) (paak bevi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) ne suna to unhon-ne bhi aik khema laga liya. subah ko jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz padh kar lautey to char khemey dekhey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya, ye kya hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko haqeeqate-haal ki itlaa di gaee. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya unhon-ne sawab ki niyat se ye nahi kya, (balke sirf aik doosre ki hirs se ye kya hai) unhein ukhaad do. main unhein achchha nahi samajhtaa, chunanche wo ukhaad diye gaey aur aap ne bhi (is saal) Ramazan mein aetikaf nahi kya. balke Shawaal ke aakhiri Ashrey mein aetikaf kya."
2042,"unhon-ne poochha, ya Rasulullah! maine jahiliyat mein nazar maana thi ke aik raat ka masjide-Haraam mein aetikaf karunga. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir apni nazar poori kar. chunanche umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne aik raat bhar aetikaf kya."
2043,"umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne zamana jahiliyat mein masjide-Haraam mein aetikaf ki nazar maana thi, Ubaid ne bayan kya ke mera khayal hai ke unhon-ne raat bhar ka zikr kya tha, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke apni nazar poori kar."
2044,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) har saal Ramazan mein das din ka aetikaf kya kartey they. lekin jis saal Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka intiqal hua, us saal Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bees din ka aetikaf kya tha."
2045,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ramazan ke aakhiri ashrey mein aetikaf ke liye zikr kya. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ijazat mangi . aap ne unhein ijazat de di, phir Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se kaha ke unke liye bhi ijazat ley dein chunanche unhon-ne aisa kar diya. jab Zenab binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anha) ne dekha to unhon-ne bhi khema lagaaney ke liye kaha, aur unke liye bhi khema laga diya gaya. unhon-ne zikr kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) subah ki Namaz ke baad apne kheme mein tashrif ley jatey aaj aapko bahut khemey dikhai diye. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye kya hai? logon ne bataya ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) , Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) , aur Zenab (Raziallahu anha) ke khemey hain. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke, bhala kya unki sawab ki niyat hai ab main bhi aetikaf nahi karunga. phir jab mahe-ramazan khatm ho gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Shawaal mein aetikaf kya."
2046,"wo haaiza hoti thin aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) masjid mein aetikaf mein hotey they, phir bhi wo aap ke sar main apne hujre hi mein kangha karti thin. aap apna sar Mubarak unki taraf badha detey."
